description.6: The Last Command, in which Grand Admiral Thrawn creates an army of clones for the Empire and Leia gives birth to twins, Jacen and Jaina Solo, destined to become powerful Jedi.
description.7: Darth Vader has a covert agent to take care of his dirty work: Jix. Vader dispatches Jix to take care of an Imperial governor who has defected to the Rebel Alliance. But Jix finds a different, more important traitor, and winds up in a one-man war against a legion of stormtroopers.
description.11: Baron Fel's wingmen-the merciless pilots of the Imperial 181st Fighter Division-are falling to the firepower of Rogue Squadron. But Fel himself is not down. He has a final card to play, and Wedge Antilles is about to fold!
description.12: The Heroes for Hire head to Lemuria to help Sersi take on Ghaur!
description.13: Daredevil and Elektra stand united against the American Samurai, unaware of the dangers that the mastermind has laid out for the former couple.
description.15: Journey into Mystery as you have NEVER seen it before! Shang-Chi, the Master of Kung Fu, returns to Hong Kong to find tranquility and balance. But already there are rumblings on the criminal underground, hushed voices that speak the name of the woman known only as the..."Cursed Lotus"!
description.17: A FAREWELL TO ARMS! Back from the dead, Spider-Man must save bystanders when Doctor Octopus topples an abandoned building and decimates the Lower East Side. Black Tarantula attacks Delilah, but heals her in an effort to send a message to the Rose.
description.18: "Inquiring Eye" reporter Irene Merryweather digs a little too deep into Sebastian Shaw’s shadowy affiliations. And now the Hellfire Club has employed their mercenaries to silence her! Thankfully, Cable’s on the scene for a daring rescue!
description.20: A dimensional rift opened up by the Technomancer Corporation brings forward a parade of gremlins!
description.24: On the run once again, the Hulk stows away on a plane to New York. But having the Hulk in such a confined space so high up is NEVER a good idea! And the situation takes a turn for the worse when Mister Hyde makes his move!
description.27: Prison break! Rogue and Gambit battle Nanny for freedom!
description.32: X-Force and Cable have gone their separate ways! Without their mysterious leader, X-Force find themselves roadtripping towards new adventures!
description.35: It all comes down to this, a showdown over the'Katana fleet. The'Rebels and'Imperials'have both located the abandoned'Dreadnaughts, and each is looking to outgun the other, take the fleet, and direct'the galaxy'to their way of thinking. Odds this round are on'Grand Admiral'Thrawn. He has a trick up his sleeve, one not seen since the end of the'Clone Wars. One that could spark a second round of the Clone Wars!
description.36: Featuring the historic confrontation between the Old Republic and the Empire, The Fall of the Sith Empire cannot end but with the victory of the Old Republic. But even winners have losses, and the Sith Empire walks away from this battle with a victory of its own... one which will later spell doom for the Old Republic.
description.46: The Hulk makes War! With his new power granted by Apocalypse, nothing seems capable of stopping Hulk in his tracks! To stop an unstoppable force, you need to find another unstoppable force! Enter the JUGGERNAUT!
description.50: As Operation Zero Tolerance rages on, Rogue, Joseph, Gambit, Spat, and Grovel find themselves in the custody of the robot called Nanny.
description.61: Rogue Squadron brings the battle to the Imperials as X-wings and TIEs zigzag among the lofty minarets of Brentaal. More than one Rogue will be shot down this day, but an X-wing pilot on the ground with a blaster is twice as angry and almost as dangerous!
description.64: It’s H4H against H4H when the Controller takes control of Iron Fist and turns him against Luke Cage!
description.65: Artist P. Craig Russell reimagines Doctor Strange's first Annual, spinning new life into a mesmerizing tale of ego, deceit, and dark magic!
description.66: Elektra foils a bank robbery only to find her ex-lover Matt Murdock also on the scene; The American Samurai makes a mysterious first appearance, and Elektra and Daredevil decide to join forces to find and capture him.
description.67: BACK FROM THE DEAD! After nearly escaping being turned into a resurrected Otto Octavius, Spider-Man breaks free, but as Stunner sacrifices himself for the resurrection ceremony, the unthinkable happens - DR. OCTOPUS IS REBORN!
description.69: The battle for an ancient Egyptian world is put to an end when Spider-Man breaks a staff and Akasha overcomes her urges!
description.72: The'Katana fleet, almost two hundred'Dreadnaught'heavy cruisers, were lost to'hyperspace'in the days of the'Old Republic. Now the'Empire'wants the cruisers so they can regain power. The'New Republic'wants the ships to crush the Empire for good. And'Talon Karrde'is the only man who knows where to find the lost fleet, which could either be an invitation to fortune,  or a bargaining chip at his execution.
description.73: The Sith invasion rages on, as the dark side of the Force takes the upper hand over the Old Republic. But Dark Lord Naga Sadow is about to learn that winning a battle is not the same as winning a war!
description.84: On the world of Brentaal, Imperial General Isoto prepares for a Rebel assault. His goal: not to save the planet, or even the Imperial base, but to save himself. Isoto has the best shield there is, the Empire's greatest fighter ace, Baron Fel. But having the Baron and having him take orders are two totally different things!
description.86: Elektra's first brush with Daredevil! Can this explosive couple leave past wounds behind them, as they track a new, dangerous vigilante?
description.87: Angered after discovering grave robbers stole Otto Octavius' body, Dr. Octupus joins forces with the Rose to resurrect Otto's body using someone else's life force. In an effort to put an end to it all, Spidey joins the raid only to become the life force sacrificed. Will he escape? Or will he be the reincarnated Otto Octavius?
description.88: After falling into a crater and dreaming of an ancient Egyptian world, Akasha travels to New York and turns into the Living Pharaoh!
description.91: Blinded by a chemical accident in his youth, young Matt Murdock tapped into his other super human senses to become the Defender of Hell's Kitchen, Daredevil!
description.96: The Hulk has been transformed...into the Horseman of Apocalypse, War! Can even the Hulk's oldest friend Rick Jones get through to him now?

0.text: The crew must band together to save Cyclops…but the X-Men stand divided!

2.text: Henrietta Rose is a victim of The Other! Silver Surfer swoops in for a rescue, and unlocks a formative memory from his earliest days on Earth!

3.text: Black Widow offers advice to Songbird and MACH-1 by telling them a tale of the first replacement Avengers.

4.text: Kitty Pryde’s first mission for S.H.I.E.L.D. involves helping an undercover spy and striking against a foe named Ogun!

5.text: New Mutants past meet the New Mutants of the present! Things get even stranger when Magik’s sinister older brother emerges from the shadows.

8.text: After Daredevil is shot by Black Widow, Karen Page struggles to nurse him back to health. Once the Man Without Fear regains his senses, he’s hot on Widow’s trail! But this manhunt isn’t without obstacle; enter Ursa Major, Soviet Russia's strangest science project!

10.text: When the X-Men’s newest friend gets activated as a Prime Sentinel, Wolverine decides the best thing to do is evacuate!  But when Cyclops gets hit in the crossfire, we discover there may be a few casualties in this war.

12.text: The Heroes for Hire head to Lemuria to help Sersi take on Ghaur!

13.text: Daredevil and Elektra stand united against the American Samurai, unaware of the dangers that the mastermind has laid out for the former couple.

14.text: Magik reunites the New Mutants to save their former selves! But wait—isn’t Magik dead?

16.text: Pietro Maximoff is Quicksilver; Avenger, son of Magneto and brother of Scarlet Witch, former member of the Brotherhood of Mutants. Not to mention, the fastest living thing on Earth! Check out Quicksilver in his solo series, and discover what adventures await Marvel’s mightiest mutant! In the first issue, Pietro wishes to turn over a new leaf in his hazard-filled life. Quicksilver becomes leader to the Knights of Wundagore!

18.text: "Inquiring Eye" reporter Irene Merryweather digs a little too deep into Sebastian Shaw’s shadowy affiliations. And now the Hellfire Club has employed their mercenaries to silence her! Thankfully, Cable’s on the scene for a daring rescue!

19.text: The Circus of Crime is in town for one night only. Can Generation X walk the tight-rope and bring the criminals to justice?

21.text: Shanna the She-Devil will soon come to realize that her relationship problems will be nothing compared to what's coming!

22.text: Venom goes AWOL after defusing a bomb implanted in his chest. Agent Smith calls on Spider-Man to bring in his “rogue agent”!

23.text: Pete Wisdom’s past comes knocking—and it may prove deadly!

28.text: The ultimate showdown between Iceman and Bastion!

30.text: The Puppet Master relives all his past wrongs, leading to a change of heart when he finally meets Mephisto.

31.text: Songbird must fight alone after all her teammates are captured by the Elements of Doom!

38.text: You've waited. You've wondered. Now you won't believe the secret of "M!"

39.text: Cable finally comes face to face with Bastion!

40.text: Galactus has arrived! How will Captain America and the other heroes defeat the World Eater? Who will live? Who will die? And will Bucky continue fighting the good fight?

41.text: Daredevil finds himself at the mercy of Omega Red! Only the villain has no mercy to give. Just as Omega Red is about to kill Daredevil, a third player enters the game; Black Widow saves Daredevil’s life with not a moment to spare. But whose side is Natasha on?

43.text: It all concludes here! And it’s a stunner! Spider-Man Vs. Green Goblin in a climactic throw down to the finish! Crime Master guest-stars.

44.text: When the X-Men realize that innocent people are being turned into Prime Sentinels, they take action. And finally—the return of Jubilee!

45.text: Wundagore and its many wonders await... but the High Evolutionary may cut Excalibur’s visit short!

49.text: It's The Fantastic Four versus Terrax, Firelord, and Plasma! And if that wasn't enough, Doctor Doom is waiting in the wings!

51.text: Bobby and Cecilia escape the Prime Sentinels with an extra assist!

53.text: The Gangers finally reveal their masterstroke to the Puppet Master, which involves their worship of the Silver Surfer. Spider-Man shows up with some bad news for Alicia regarding her stepfather.

54.text: The Thunderbolts defy Citizen V's orders and track down the Elements of Doom. The results will be disastrous!

56.text: Galactus has arrived! It is time for Tony Stark to be the hero he was born to be. But what if he has to work with Doctor Doom to do it?

57.text: The X-Force is on the road following Cable to his safehouse! But could a disagreement break up the gang forever?

60.text: Colossus is pulled into Arcade's Murderworld alongside Excalibur’s Meggan!

62.text: Daniel Rand’s transformation into Iron Fist was born of tragedy, self-discovery, and enlightenment.  In this eye-opening issue of Uncanny Origins, the Immortal Iron Fist’s past is laid out in full. Who has influenced Daniel Rand to become the hero he is today? And what dark threats lurk on his horizon?

64.text: It’s H4H against H4H when the Controller takes control of Iron Fist and turns him against Luke Cage!

65.text: Artist P. Craig Russell reimagines Doctor Strange's first Annual, spinning new life into a mesmerizing tale of ego, deceit, and dark magic!

66.text: Elektra foils a bank robbery only to find her ex-lover Matt Murdock also on the scene; The American Samurai makes a mysterious first appearance, and Elektra and Daredevil decide to join forces to find and capture him.

68.text: The secret of the Dark Hunter is revealed? And what does it have to do with Franklin's mutant powers?

70.text: Ka-Zar plays a not-so-fun game of Hide and Seek…with the Rhino!

71.text: Venom and Ghost Rider are after the same villain, but who will win the fight to claim them as their prey?

75.text: Daredevil, caught in a riot at Ryker’s Island! Mr. Fear has flooded the prison with his fear gas, but before Daredevil can face Fear, he must take down a new Gladiator. And this one is deadlier than the last.

78.text: After the X-Men escape from Bastions base, Wolverine makes a huge discovery and reveals the secret of the Prime Sentinels!

80.text: From out of the fire, comes a savior… But who is it?

81.text: Cable's next target is Zero Tolerance leader Bastion!

82.text: Captain America battles it out with...Nick Fury?

83.text: It's See-Threepio and Artoo-Detoo saving the planet Tahlboor, in an adventure set years before Star Wars: A New Hope!

85.text: When one door closes, another one opens. Hercules takes a leave of absence to deal with his excessive drinking, while Luke Cage joins the team full time!

86.text: Elektra's first brush with Daredevil! Can this explosive couple leave past wounds behind them, as they track a new, dangerous vigilante?

89.text: Ka-Zar is finally able to see his brother again! However, the Rhino is coming to crash the reunion.

90.text: When faced with a terrorist, the U.S. government sends Venom to the scene to save the day.

92.text: Spider-Man and Generation X team-up! Can they neutralize the would-be-terrorists known as D.E.A.D.?

94.text: Typhoid Mary guest-stars in a plot to foil Daredevil!

95.text: Meggan’s life is on the line in a “Question of Survival!”

99.text: During a quiet afternoon in Central Park, The Fantastic Four are attacked by none other than Terrax! Plus, a new member is added to Marvel's Finest Family.
